BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, May 10 (KCNA) -- The great leader 
President Kim Il-song Monday sent a wreath to the bier of Yi 
Tong-chun, member of the Central Committee of the Workers' Party 
of Korea and deputy to the Supreme People's Assembly of the 
Democratic People's Republic of Korea, expressing deep 
condolences over his death. 
  Yi Tong-chun died on May 8 at the age of 61. 
  He devotedly worked at responsible posts of central and 
local 
party organizations and party organizations of the army to 
defend the party and the leader and firmly build up the party 
ranks. 

